If you're ready to start a healing circle and learn how to connect to other women, talk about intimacy, and build relationship with others, the Black Girl Healing Circle Directory is here!

Search for women in your area, women who are wanting to start virtually only groups, and learn more about who you're connecting with. 

Join for FREE by going to BlackGirlHealingCircles.com and get the free guide.
